Benjamin assumed the throne in the {{YearlinkName|1273}}, after the mysterious disappearance of his father.

In the [[1291 DR|eighteenth year of his reign]], an enormous and unexplained explosion rocked the island of [[Flamsterd]].{{Cite dragon/362/Grand History of the Realms: The Moonshaes|30}}

Benjamin ruled for a total of twenty-three years before he was assassinated by nobles from [[Ogden]] in the {{YearlinkName|1296}}.
